<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_269876eeea14.aspx"><b>小雅·桑扈</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson269876eeea14">
<p>交交桑扈，有莺其羽。君子乐胥，受天之祜。</p>
<p>交交桑扈，有莺其领。君子乐胥，万邦之屏。</p>
<p>之屏之翰，百辟为宪。不戢不难，受福不那。</p>
<p>兕觥其觩，旨酒思柔。彼交匪敖，万福来求。</p>
</div>
